{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/Discord.png?t=1734565853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Early in the 23rd century, years of anarchy turned the planet into a violent wasteland. Civilization withdrew to the planet's remote areas and established Outposts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To keep the economy running, raids are organized into the Wasteland to gather supplies, valuables, and weapons. These raids are known as <strong>Blood Runs</strong> due to their brutal nature and high risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Those who undertake these raids go by the name <strong>Blood Runners</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/Combat.gif?t=1734565853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Every Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a randomly generated world, no two runs will be the same. Explore the maps, each with unique locations featuring constantly changing environments, randomized loot locations, and layouts. Learn to navigate the wasteland and survive long enough to uncover the secrets of each map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/Modding.gif?t=1734565853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gun Modding</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Raid the wastelands in a way that matches your playstyle. With fully modular guns, you can mix and match to make yourself the most formidable Blood Runner in the wasteland. Spec into recoil control and accuracy for the calculated and methodical, or choose the run and gun approach with high-damage and ergonomics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/Quests.gif?t=1734565853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Quests &amp; Looting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Between runs, you'll explore Outpost 072 and embark on various quests that take you through the world. You'll uncover secrets and stories about the world by meeting intriguing characters. With over 200 unique items to collect, you can craft new items, upgrade your base, and trade with merchants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/Base___Skills.gif?t=1734565853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock Skills &amp; Upgrade Your Base</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up to unlock skill points, which can be used to level up skills, giving you a distinct edge in the wasteland. Craft new building units and decorations to make your base your own. Level up building units to unlock crafting, repairing, permanent perks, and storage space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734565853","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/page.bg.jpg?t=1734565853","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/86cf1cc0d626de33689b097efc38ce03ea4d6c5d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734565853","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/86cf1cc0d626de33689b097efc38ce03ea4d6c5d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734565853","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto